"NOWPayments allows you to accept credit card payments directly to your "
"crypto wallet. Funds go straight to your wallet – no middleman."
msgstr ""
"NOWPayments te permite aceptar pagos con tarjeta de crédito directamente a "
"tu billetera cripto. Los fondos van directamente a tu billetera, sin "
"intermediario."

